{
  "texts": [
    "We apply natural language generation tools to extractive summaries to obtain their abstractive version.",
    "Thus, the summarized sentences are distinct from the original set of sentences.",
    "The summarised document's contents are different from the initial set of sentences in the original document.",
    "Both abstractive and extractive rules are applied in the hybrid summarization, hence the hybrid name for the summarization technique.All three summarization techniques employ stylistic and syntactic rules to obtain summaries.",
    "Standard features used are the relative position of the sentence, length of the sentences, and presence of verb phrases and noun phrases."
  ]
}